#
# This file outlines the database schema to be used in the SQLite
# database backend for this script.
#
# Author: Daniel Hawkins
# Last Modified: 2015-06-04
#

Table       Field           Type            Nullable        PK      FK      FK_To_Table
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Book        BookID          int             N               Y       N       -
Book        Title           varchar(30)     N               N       N       -
Book        Subtitle        varchar(60)     Y               N       N       -
Book        Year            shortint        Y               N       N       -
Book        TypeID          tinyint         N               N       Y       Type

BookOwner   BookID          int             N               Y       Y       Book
BookOwner   OwnerID         int             N               Y       Y       Owner
BookOwner   Quantity        smallint        N               N       N       -

Owner       OwnerID         int             N               Y       N       -
Owner       LastName        varchar(30)     N               N       N       -
Owner       FirstName       varchar(30)     N               N       N       -

BookGenre   BookID          int             N               Y       Y       Book
BookGenre   GenreID         int             N               Y       Y       Genre

Genre       GenreID         int             N               Y       N       -
Genre       GenreName       varchar(20)     N               N       N       -

Type        TypeID          int             N               Y       N       -
Type        TypeName        char(9)         N               N       N       -

BookAuthor  BookID          int             N               Y       Y       Book
BookAuthor  AuthorID        int             N               Y       Y       Author
BookAuthor  AuthorOrder     smallint        Y               N       N       -

Author      AuthorID        int             N               Y       N       -
Author      AuthorLast      varchar(30)     N               N       N       -
Author      AuthorFirst     varchar(30)     N               N       N       -
Author      AuthorMiddle    varchar(30)     N               N       N       -
